item.description:
Sooo This month- is at Jeff! Yes again, he's given us a nice home to meet at- thank you Jeff!

This month let's talk about fun stuff... Places we have traveled to and Photographed! Bring your favorite stories, images or prints of the places you have been. Share!

Bring prints, bring cameras, bring your smart wit and humor! Mix it all up- what have you got? August's Photo Meet Up at Jeff Bakers place! Anyone need directions? Just click the blue link that says "Visions by Baker" to see where to go...


See you there!
Donna
